column10:
I was on the top of the list of guys that did not recommend this game in about 1 year ago, But now I see huge difference , developers show that they are working hard to regain battlefield series reputation : 
- Great Updates ;
- Wonderful optimization ;
- Excellent ambient ;
* Now I recommend this game .

it's a battlefield game!

even though the game is lacking in map and weapon variety, released in a horrible state and is overall much weaker than past entries in the series.

if you like battlefield you will get your enjoyment out of this game. however, for the love of god, DON'T PAY FULL PRICE FOR IT! it's okay for 20$ or less. And of course don't pay for microtransactions and battle passes (the cancer of modern gaming)
